  initial_dgca:"Has successfully completed ground school instruction required by the Initial Flight Dispatcher Course training as prescribed in ICAO Doc 10106, ICAO Doc 9868 and EASA Part ORO.GEN.110(c).",
  initial_easa:"Has successfully completed the Flight Dispatcher Initial Training delivered in English in accordance with ICAO Doc 10106, ICAO Doc 9868, EASA Part ORO.GEN.110(c) and IOSA ISM Table 3.6",
  recurrent:"Has successfully completed the Flight Dispatch Recurrent Training delivered in English in accordance with ICAO Doc 10106, ICAO Doc 9868, EASA Part ORO.GEN.110(c) and IOSA ISM Table 3.6",
